         <abstract>
            <p>Let $S^k_n$ be the nonlinear spline manifold of order $k$ and with $n - k$ interior variable knots. We prove that all best $L_2\lbrack 0, 1 \rbrack$ approximants from $S^k_n$ to a continuous function on $\lbrack 0, 1 \rbrack$ also continuous there. We also prove that there exists a $C^\infty \lbrack 0, 1 \rbrack$ function with no $C^2\lbrack 0, 1 \rbrack$ best $L_ \lbrack 0, 1 \rbrack$ approximants from $S^k_n$.</p>
          </abstract>
